title: Prime drinks are going viral in real life. It’s all about status.
description: Prime drinks have become the “it” product for teens, thanks to the power of online influencers.

title: SpaceX set to launch its 6th full astronaut crew to the space station
description: SpaceX's planned launch will carry two NASA astronuats as well as one from the United Arab Emirates and a Russian cosmonaut for a six-month stay at the International Space Station.

title: Musk defends ‘Dilbert’ creator, says media is ‘racist against whites’
description: The Tesla and Twitter chief blasted media outlets for dropping Scott Adams' cartoon following Adams' racist rant against Black people.

title: Instagram users are being served gory videos of killing and torture
description: The videos have become away for meme pages to up their engagement, helping them raise their income from advertising.

title: Biden finds breaking up Big Tech is hard to do
description: Time is ticking on an ambitious antitrust agenda, as modern-day trustbusters like the FTC's Lina Khan meet resistance from industry, Congress and the courts.
